---
title: Butternut Squash Risotto with chilli and cheese
description: This butternut squash risotto is bright and beautiful both to look at and to taste. Filled with veg, cheese, and a hint of gentle spice, this is a restaurant-worthy dish you'll be amazed you made yourself.
